name: RVD
description: The Whole F'n Show, RVD is a high-flying daredevil with a unique blend of martial arts and aerial maneuvers. Known for his laid-back attitude and innovative moves like the Van Daminator and the Five-Star Frog Splash.

name: John Cena
description: The Face That Runs the Place, John Cena is a powerhouse with a never-give-up attitude. His signature moves like the Attitude Adjustment and the STF have made him a legend in the ring.

name: Chris Jericho
description: The Ayatollah of Rock 'n' Rolla, Chris Jericho is a master of reinvention. With a blend of technical prowess and showmanship, he's won titles across multiple promotions and is a true icon of the industry.

name: Stone Cold Steve Austin
description: The Texas Rattlesnake, Stone Cold Steve Austin is the embodiment of rebellion. With his Stunner and his 'Austin 3:16' catchphrase, he became the face of the Attitude Era and a cultural phenomenon.

name: CM Punk
description: The Voice of the Voiceless, CM Punk is a straight-edge superstar with a gift for gab. His Pipe Bomb promo and his 434-day WWE Championship reign solidified his place in wrestling history.

name: The Rock
description: The People's Champion, The Rock is a charismatic powerhouse with a knack for entertainment. His Rock Bottom and People's Elbow, along with his electrifying promos, have made him a global icon.

name: Triple H
description: The Game, Triple H is a cerebral assassin with a pedigree for success. His sledgehammer and his strategic mind have helped him dominate the ring and become a wrestling legend.

name: Randy Orton
description: The Viper, Randy Orton is a third-generation superstar with a lethal RKO. His cunning and ruthless nature have made him one of the most dangerous competitors in wrestling.

name: Edge
description: The Rated-R Superstar, Edge is an opportunistic daredevil with a penchant for the extreme. His Spear and his TLC matches have cemented his legacy as a hardcore legend.

name: Shawn Michaels
description: The Showstopper, Shawn Michaels is a charismatic performer with unparalleled in-ring skills. His Sweet Chin Music and his Mr. WrestleMania moniker speak to his ability to deliver on the grandest stage.

name: Bret Hart
description: The Excellence of Execution, Bret Hart is a technical master with a sharpshooter submission. His storytelling and in-ring psychology have made him one of the greatest of all time.

name: Kurt Angle
description: The Olympic Hero, Kurt Angle is a wrestling machine with a gold medal pedigree. His Ankle Lock and his intensity have made him a force to be reckoned with in the ring.

name: Brock Lesnar
description: The Beast Incarnate, Brock Lesnar is a powerhouse with a suplex city residency. His F5 and his sheer dominance have made him one of the most feared competitors in wrestling.

name: Roman Reigns
description: The Tribal Chief, Roman Reigns is a dominant force with a spear that can end any match. His leadership and his ability to perform under pressure have made him a top star.

name: Seth Rollins
description: The Architect, Seth Rollins is a visionary with a curb stomp that can change the game. His innovative style and his ability to reinvent himself have made him a standout performer.

name: Dean Ambrose
description: The Lunatic Fringe, Dean Ambrose is an unpredictable wild card with a penchant for chaos. His Dirty Deeds and his fearless attitude have made him a fan favorite.

name: The Miz
description: The A-Lister, The Miz is a charismatic talker with a Skull-Crushing Finale. His ability to entertain and his never-say-die attitude have made him a mainstay in wrestling.

name: Dolph Ziggler
description: The Showoff, Dolph Ziggler is an athletic marvel with a Zig Zag that can come out of nowhere. His resilience and his ability to perform at a high level have earned him respect.

name: Jeff Hardy
description: The Charismatic Enigma, Jeff Hardy is a high-flying artist with a Swanton Bomb that defies gravity. His creativity and his willingness to take risks have made him a legend.

name: Big E
description: The Powerhouse of Positivity, Big E is a charismatic strongman with a Big Ending that can flatten opponents. His humor and his strength have made him a fan favorite.

name: Gunther
description: The Ring General, Gunther is a hard-hitting technician with a devastating chop. His dominance and his ability to control the ring have made him a force to be reckoned with.

name: Kevin Owens
description: The Prizefighter, Kevin Owens is a brawling trash-talker with a Stunner that can end any match. His tenacity and his ability to get under his opponents' skin have made him a standout.

name: Finn Balor
description: The Demon King, Finn Balor is a versatile performer with a Coup de Gr√¢ce that can finish any opponent. His ability to transform into the demon has added a unique element to his character.

name: AJ Styles
description: The Phenomenal One, AJ Styles is a wrestling virtuoso with a Styles Clash that can win any match. His ability to adapt and his consistent excellence have made him a legend.

name: Cody Rhodes
description: The American Nightmare, Cody Rhodes is a passionate performer with a Cross Rhodes that can end any match. His dedication to the craft and his ability to tell a story have made him a fan favorite.

name: Rey Mysterio
description: The Ultimate Underdog, Rey Mysterio is a high-flying luchador with a 619 that can surprise any opponent. His heart and his ability to overcome the odds have made him a legend.

name: JBL
description: The Wrestling God, JBL is a hard-hitting Texan with a Clothesline from Hell. His business acumen and his in-ring brutality have made him a memorable character.

name: Eddie Guerrero
description: Latino Heat, Eddie Guerrero is a charismatic technician with a Frog Splash that honors his legacy. His ability to lie, cheat, and steal his way to victory made him a beloved figure.

name: Booker T
description: The Five-Time WCW Champion, Booker T is an athletic entertainer with a Scissor Kick that can cut through the competition. His charisma and his in-ring skills have made him a fan favorite.

name: Shinsuke Nakamura
description: The King of Strong Style, Shinsuke Nakamura is a charismatic striker with a Kinshasa that can end any match. His unorthodox style and his ability to captivate the audience have made him a standout.

name: The Undertaker
description: The Phenom, The Undertaker is a legendary figure with a supernatural aura. His Tombstone Piledriver and his undefeated streak at WrestleMania have made him an icon of the industry.

name: Ric Flair
description: The Nature Boy, Ric Flair is a flamboyant stylist with a Figure-Four Leglock that has submitted many opponents. His 'Woo!' catchphrase and his incredible career spanning decades have made him a wrestling icon.

name: Daniel Bryan
description: The Yes Man, Daniel Bryan is a technical wizard with a Running Knee that can knock out any opponent. His underdog story and his 'Yes!' movement have made him a beloved figure in wrestling.
